{"TopicId":142317,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Bing back the \u0027Escape\u0027 Key in time warp mode","CreatedByName":"lodger","CreatedById":126565,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T06:27:20Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"lodger","CreatedById":126565,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T06:27:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhatever the reasons were to change the mapping of the \u0027Escape\u0027 key in time warp mode to \u0027/\u0027 (forward slash) - please change it back to the way it was in all the previous versions. Please!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DD_bwest","CreatedById":164906,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T06:35:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyou can change it in settings...\u00A0\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GeneCash","CreatedById":81605,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T06:36:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like better this way, as it\u0027s right next to the other time warp controls.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lodger","CreatedById":126565,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T06:40:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222643116\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466663725\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022164906\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DD_bwest\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, DD_bwest said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyou can change it in settings...\u00A0\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAaaah, okay - I\u00A0didn\u0027t know that. Thanks, dude! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222643117\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466663773\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002281605\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GeneCash\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, GeneCash said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like better this way, as it\u0027s right next to the other time warp controls.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDepends on wether you are using an english / US or non-english / non-US keyboard. In my case (german keyboard setup), I\u0027d rather prefer it the \u0027old\u0027 way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-23T06:42:08Z\u0022 title=\u002206/23/2016 06:42  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 23, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by lodger\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hodari","CreatedById":157578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T07:27:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think it was a bad change, but it is certainly one that will take some getting used to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}